@SB8.5 = Ethics of the Pur<193><207>as
Dharma or duty constitutes the foundation of pur<193><207>ic ethics. ç
It embraces all the factors which contribute to the progress and well-being ç
of the individual, the society and the world at large. These factors ç
include the possession of gu<207>as or virtues and karma or proper ç
